                        <div class="card-badge blue">Customer Name #1</div>

                        <p class="card-text">
                            Job Works are new Projects (work orders). You can add new product entry (product being used for this job-work) using the "New Entry" button. The "View More" displays a list of Entries as well as details aboout the job work.
                        </p>

                        <div class="divider card-divider"></div>

                        <ul class="revenue-list">

                            <li class="revenue-item icon-box">

                                <button class="btn btn-dashing" data-load-more>
                                    <span class="spiner"></span>

